    Wedding trends for 2018

    Colours As we already know the Pantone Colour of the year is Ultra Violet, so this will certainly feature quite heavily. Bright and bold colours will make their way into wedding designs this year, in particular gorgeous jewel tones such a ruby, sapphire and emerald. Rose gold has been huge in 2017 and metallics are still going strong with copper and silver.
